url: "https://github.com/robotrocketscience/aelfrice"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - artificial intelligence
  - agent memory
  - Bayesian inference
  - Beta-Bernoulli
  - retrieval-augmented generation
  - Model Context Protocol
  - SQLite
  - FTS5
